HEADWORD: Lyme grass
<hw>Lyme" grass`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A coarse perennial grass of several species of <gen>Elymus</gen>,
esp. <spn>Elymus Canadensis</spn>, and the European <spn>Elymus
arenarius</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lymph</ent>⟦br⟧
